{
  "stem": "1736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 348.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the fact was that we were now 13 years of age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a few girls that were a little bit older, but altogether there were about 55 kids.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All over Germany, in this home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the regime boss-- we were-- in charge was a youth leader, a Jewish person, who was in fact the son of a Hamburg rabbi.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, not long after that, my sister got the same advice, and she was sent to a similar institution in a place called Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, you may remember Magdeburg was very prominent recently in the overthrow of the German communist regime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this is just bringing it up-to-date to tell you where it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was sort of the thing that they were doing and separating families, and she was sent there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few months later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'll stay with my story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And being 13, or between the age of 13 and 14, we started going to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a Jewish day school in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the idea was that we'd go to school half a day, and we would, you know, do social study or whatever for the rest of the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we started--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes, but not to the effect-- you know, we-- we kept some-- we were getting further and further away from it because there--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just not the opportunity to do these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had amongst our children-- the children came from all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were some of them that didn't even know they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came there simply because the authorities had decided that their great-grandfather was Jewish or their great-grandmother was Jewish, and therefore they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
